query: SELECT DATE_FORMAT(identificationDate, '%Y-%m') as month, COUNT(*) as count FROM non_conformities WHERE identificationDate >= '2025-07-06' GROUP BY DATE_FORMAT(identificationDate, '%Y-%m') ORDER BY DATE_FORMAT(identificationDate, '%Y-%m') LIMIT 10;
